title: [Frostmain Docks, Greying Pier]
[Frostmain, Docks]
description: The skeletal remains of a waterfowl hang in a rusted cage that is suspended from a nearby post.  To the north, the starboard tine of the trident-shaped docks thrusts into the cruel waters of the main.  Set rocking by the breeze, the cage's grating creaks are the only sounds approximating birdsong.
